reviews.review_text: Great cafe with very good music and delicious desserts. Interesting food and friendly team. The appearance of the ambience is also successful and very appealing. From the disadvantages I can list very bad (too strongly roasted coffee) and somewhat expensive prices. But I would like to visit this cafe again because of the desserts. They are to be recommended.
